description:
I got some practice in at Harmony Bends to prepare for Amateur Worlds 2025! 
Thank you to my sponsor: https://www.instagram.com/chainreactions_discgolf/ 
It's bhirdietime!
For more of my disc golf journey follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bhirdietime/
